        <div class="cdm-cs-icon">&#x1F6E1;</div>
        <p>
          This product has undergone a formal clinical risk management process in accordance with <strong>NHS Digital standard DCB 0129</strong>. All identified hazards have been assessed and mitigated to a level that is <strong>As Low As Reasonably Practicable (ALARP)</strong>.
        </p>
